title: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description:
Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.

Steps to reproduce:
1. Open the report containing a table with highlight/map.
2. Export the data in the table.

OB: When attempting to export data from a table containing highlight/map, an exception is thrown.
EB: The data in the table should be successfully exported.
SR: 1. Open the report with the table containing highlight/map. 2. Try to export the data from the table and confirm that it is exported without any exceptions.
